OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FThe UK and Irish governments' long-
OL,7,Fawaited framework to deal with the
OL,8,Flegacy of the Northern Ireland
OL,9,FTroubles is founded on "reciprocal
OL,10,Fcooperation", the Tanaiste will say
OL,11,Flater.
OL,13,FSimon Harris will join Northern
OL,14,FIreland Secretary Hilary Benn on
OL,15,FFriday afternoon to formally unveil
OL,16,Fthe proposals, which have been
OL,17,Fdeveloped following substantive
OL,18,Fengagement between the two governments.
