OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FMr Harris is expected to describe the
OL,7,Fframework as a "night and day
OL,8,Fimprovement" on the previous
OL,9,Fmechanisms introduced unilaterally by
OL,10,Fthe previous UK government.
OL,12,FThe new framework, which includes
OL,13,Fcommitments to fundamentally reform
OL,14,Fthe mechanisms established in the 2023
OL,15,FLegacy Act, will raise expectations
OL,16,Fthat the Irish Government is moving
OL,17,Fcloser to dropping its interstate
OL,18,Flegal case against the UK.
