OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FLabour came to power with a pledge to
OL,7,Freplace and repeal the 2023 Legacy Act
OL,8,Fintroduced by the Conservatives, which
OL,9,Fhalted scores of civil cases and
OL,10,Finquests into Troubles deaths.
OL,12,FThe Act was opposed by victims' groups
OL,13,Fand political parties in Northern
OL,14,FIreland, and it led the Dublin
OL,15,Fgovernment to launch an interstate
OL,16,Flegal case against the UK claiming it
OL,17,Fbreached the European Convention on
OL,18,FHuman Rights (ECHR).
