OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FThe legislation created a new legacy
OL,7,Fbody, the Independent Commission for
OL,8,FReconciliation and Information
OL,9,FRecovery (ICRIR), to take over the
OL,10,Finvestigation of all outstanding
OL,11,FTroubles cases.
OL,13,FThe Act also contained an offer of
OL,14,Fconditional immunity to some suspects
OL,15,Fbut this was disapplied after legal
OL,16,Faction by bereaved families.
OL,18,FThe new framework is closer to the
OL,19,Fdetails of the Stormont House
OL,20,FAgreement of 2014, which were never
OL,21,Fimplemented.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
