OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FIt will see the ICRIR fundamentally
OL,7,Freformed to become a Legacy
OL,8,FCommission, which will investigate
OL,9,FTroubles deaths.
OL,11,FA separate body will be created to
OL,12,Fdeal with information recovery.
OL,14,FThere are no proposals for amnesties
OL,15,Ffor suspects within the new framework.
OL,17,FIt is understood the framework will
OL,18,Finclude the following measures:
