OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,F` Removal of the bar on legacy-related
OL,7,Fcivil cases in UK courts and allow the
OL,8,Fresumption of inquests that were
OL,9,Fhalted by the Legacy Act. Inquests
OL,10,Fthat had not been started before the
OL,11,FLegacy Act's legal guillotine came
OL,12,Finto force will be reviewed to
OL,13,Festablish the best way forward.
