OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,F` Significant restructuring of the
OL,7,FICRIR. It will be renamed the Legacy
OL,8,FCommission. There will be two co-equal
OL,9,Fdirectors of investigations. A
OL,10,Fstatutory independent oversight board
OL,11,Fwill be created along with an advisory
OL,12,Fgroup made up of victims and
OL,13,Fsurvivors. An independent panel will
OL,14,Falso advise on senior appointments to
OL,15,Fthe commission. Measures will be
OL,16,Fintroduced to identify any conflict of
OL,17,Finterest issues within the commission.
OL,19,F` The commission will be empowered to
OL,20,Fcarry out investigations capable of
OL,21,Fleading to prosecutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
