OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,F` Independent judges will hold
OL,7,Finquisitorial public hearings, with
OL,8,Fvictims' families able to participate.
OL,10,F` A separate truth recovery mechanism
OL,11,Fwill be created called the Independent
OL,12,FCommission on Information Retrieval.
OL,13,FThis will be a jointly funded UK/Irish
OL,14,Fcross-border body that will initially
OL,15,Foperate on a pilot basis.
