OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,F` Reform of disclosure processes to
OL,7,Faddress concerns over a controversial
OL,8,Fveto power held by the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Secretary of State on what
OL,10,Fsensitive information can be accessed
OL,11,Fby legacy bodies.
OL,13,F` The Irish Government will commit to
OL,14,F"fullest possible cooperate" with the
OL,15,Fnew Legacy Commission.
OL,17,F` A new dedicated Legacy Unit will be
OL,18,Fcreated within the Irish police force,
OL,19,FAn Garda Siochana.
