OL,6,F` The Irish Government will also ring-
OL,7,Ffence 25 million euros to support
OL,8,Fvictims and survivors in participating
OL,9,Fand engaging with legacy bodies.
OL,11,FThe two governments believe the new
OL,12,Fframework includes proposals which are
OL,13,FECHR compliant and are capable of
OL,14,Fsecuring the support of victims and
OL,15,Fbereaved families.
