OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FMr Harris is expected to say later:
OL,7,F"Vitally, at the heart of this
OL,8,Fframework, is a commitment by the two
OL,9,Fgovernments to reciprocal cooperation.
OL,10,FWe can only comprehensively address
OL,11,Fthe legacy of the Troubles if we do so
OL,12,Facross both jurisdictions. Reciprocity
OL,13,Fis what will make this framework work
OL,14,Fand deliver for families."
OL,16,FHe will credit the joint agreement as
OL,17,Fcreating a moment of "imperfect
OL,18,Fopportunity".
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@ZO]yD@VOUzD@LO]
