OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,F"I hope that victims and families see
OL,7,Fin this deal a set of substantive
OL,8,Fcommitments, that leave behind the
OL,9,Fflawed Legacy Act, and that are
OL,10,Fgenuinely designed to provide answers
OL,11,Ffor victims, survivors and families,"
OL,12,Fhe will say.
OL,14,F"I hope that you will give the
OL,15,Freformed Legacy Commission an
OL,16,Fopportunity to deliver for you.
OL,18,F"And I hope that you will hold our
OL,19,Ffeet to the fire. I hope you will hold
OL,20,Fus accountable for delivering every
OL,21,Fparagraph of this framework.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@eO]vD@AOUzD@AOU
