OL,3,CNew Troubles legacy framework founded
OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,F"I have heard over and over again that
OL,7,Fno one wants their children, and
OL,8,Fgrandchildren, to live with trauma and
OL,9,Fpain for another generation.
OL,11,F"As a father, I understand this
OL,12,Fviscerally.
OL,14,F"Today's package gives us a chance to
OL,15,Fend this cycle. I believe, in my heart
OL,16,Fof hearts, that this is our best, and
OL,17,Flast, opportunity. We have to grasp
OL,18,Fit. It would be very wrong not to do
OL,19,Fso."
