OL,4,Con 'reciprocal cooperation'
OL,6,FThe framework will require new
OL,7,Flegislation at both Westminster and at
OL,8,Fthe Dail.
OL,10,FBoth governments have carried out
OL,11,Fconsultation with victims' groups and
OL,12,Ffamilies and will continue to do so
OL,13,Fonce the framework is published.
OL,15,FIt is understood the UK government
OL,16,Falso intends to publish separate
OL,17,Fmeasures aimed at offering protections
OL,18,Fto witnesses participating in
OL,19,FTroubles' related probes.
