OL,6,FThere will be specific measures
OL,7,Fdesigned for veterans, such as the
OL,8,Fability for them to participate or
OL,9,Fgive evidence remotely from Great
OL,10,FBritain, without having to travel back
OL,11,Fto Northern Ireland.
